Phase of Operation: TAKEOFF - ROLL/RUN
Findings
3. DIRECTIONAL CONTROL - NOT POSSIBLE - PILOT IN COMMAND
4. GROUND LOOP/SWERVE - UNCONTROLLED - PILOT IN COMMAND
----------
Occurrence #3: NOSE OVER
Phase of Operation: TAKEOFF
Findings
5. (F) TERRAIN CONDITION - WET
6. (F) TERRAIN CONDITION - SOFT
